                This component renders an accordion element, providing a visually appealing way to toggle the visibility 
                of content sections. Users can click on the title area to expand or collapse the content.
            </p>
        </header>
        <SectionTab titles={basicTitle} slotName={['preview', 'component', 'css']} class='h-[19.8rem]'>
